title: Git Training
description: Mindmajix has specially designed this Git Training Course to advance your skills for a successful career in this domain. The trainee will go through the various aspects of Git source control system, workflow, manage files with Git, and more related source control concepts. Upon completion of this online training, the trainee will hold a solid understanding and hands-on experience with Git.
